---
<section class="bg-muted py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-4xl">
        Local Courts We Handle
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
        Our attorneys regularly represent clients in courts throughout Jamestown and Chautauqua County. 
        Learn more about the courts where criminal and civil cases are handled.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <a href="/courts/jamestown-city-court" class="group">
        <div class="h-full rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">🏛</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
            Jamestown City Court
            <span class="inline-block text-sm opacity-0 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:opacity-100">
              →
            </span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Handles many misdemeanor criminal cases, traffic violations, and preliminary hearings for felony cases in Jamestown.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/courts/chautauqua-county-court" class="group">
        <div class="h-full rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">🏛</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
            Chautauqua County Court
            <span class="inline-block text-sm opacity-0 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:opacity-100">
              →
            </span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Handles felony criminal cases and higher-level matters for Chautauqua County.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/courts/dunkirk-city-court" class="group">
        <div class="h-full rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="mb-2 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">🏛</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
            Dunkirk City Court
            <span class="inline-block text-sm opacity-0 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:opacity-100">
              →
            </span>
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Local court serving Dunkirk handling criminal misdemeanors, traffic violations, and preliminary hearings.
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a 
        href="/guides/criminal-case-process-new-york" 
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-primary hover:underline"
      >
        Learn more about how local courts handle criminal cases
        <span class="text-xs">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

